Diagram 1 (Correct)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's placement at 1 is a sharp move stabbing black's vital point.
\par
\par White is aiming at creating a shortage of liberties hidden in the shape of the three black \'a1\'e3 stones.
\par
\par This one move leaves black dead.
\par
