Diagram 3 (If it was a real game)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If this were a real game, it might have been easy for white to thoughtlessly play dansu at 1. Black responds by making a hanging connection at 2 and lives.
\par
\par Both players might have thought this result was common sense, but that is mistaken.
\par }
